title: Employee Satisfaction Survey
description: A survey to measure employee satisfaction and gather feedback on workplace conditions and management.
questionOne: On a scale of 1-10, how satisfied are you with your current work environment?
questionTwo: What aspects of your job do you find most fulfilling?
questionThree: Are there any specific areas where you believe improvement is needed?

title: Customer Feedback Survey
description: Gather customer opinions and feedback to improve products and services. Understand customer satisfaction and expectations.
questionOne: How likely are you to recommend our products/services to others?
questionTwo: What features or improvements would you like to see in our products?
questionThree: How satisfied are you with the customer service you've received?

title: Health and Wellness Survey
description: An assessment of health and wellness habits to promote a healthier lifestyle. Gather information on diet, exercise, and mental health.
questionOne: How many days a week do you engage in physical exercise?
questionTwo: Do you follow a specific diet or eating plan?
questionThree: How would you rate your overall mental well-being?

title: Environmental Awareness Survey
description: Collect data on environmental awareness, habits, and opinions. Identify areas for improvement in sustainable practices.
questionOne: How often do you recycle household waste?
questionTwo: Are you conscious of your water and electricity consumption?
questionThree: What environmental issues do you consider most important?

title: Technology Usage Survey
description: Explore how people use technology in their daily lives. Gather insights into device preferences, internet usage, and tech trends.
questionOne: Which devices do you use most frequently in your daily life?
questionTwo: How many hours per day do you spend on the internet?
questionThree: What emerging technologies are you most interested in?

title: Education Feedback Survey
description: Gather feedback from students and teachers to improve the education system. Assess teaching methods, curriculum, and overall satisfaction.
questionOne: How would you rate the effectiveness of the current curriculum?
questionTwo: What teaching methods do you find most engaging?
questionThree: Are there any subjects or topics you feel are not adequately covered?

title: Social Media Usage Survey
description: Explore social media habits and preferences. Gather insights into platform usage, content preferences, and online interaction.
questionOne: Which social media platforms do you use regularly?
questionTwo: What type of content do you find most interesting on social media?
questionThree: How often do you engage with others through social media?
